{"tid":481808,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手求教] 用NAS set 無harddisk系統","createTime":"2017-11-27T14:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:29:30.000Z","uid":29021,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fde84f40ef0fe0d251b9c014fcf619e1a84a641","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"好啦，簡介吓我而家要做嘅嘢就係喺屋企set兩部電腦，不過budget有限打算唔買harddisk亦唔諗住買Windows<br />\n<br />\n咁手頭上有部NAS，所以就諗可唔可以PXE + NFS/DRBL做無硬碟系統開機，咁google過都有啲成功例子<br />\n<br />\n咁雖然以前用開ubuntu但係聽聞佢個朵臭晒，所以我又諗不如轉投openSUSE啦，咁所以啱啱開始著手整啦，呢個時候發現原來個個都淨係做iSCSI<br />\n<br />\n雖然話DSM係Linux，照計SSH Shell應該可以搞，但係DRBL好似好複雜咁，更何況NFS本身唔駛搞咁多嘢應該不成問題，而家只係剩低boot img同os img要點config<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以<del>屌吓我等我可以茅塞頓開</del>指點吓迷津？"},{"pid":"f21bee7937b4faf309e5bef85df0f9b5c70291ab","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27f0ed1756e373e04dfca2e025bdc2ca8e44006","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1eebef8fff4a68e2c1fc9779efa5a02c59c64c3f","tid":481808,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"用usb手指啦"},{"pid":"46e355cf9102f443454d0d4ef2641726d9c2098f","tid":481808,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:51:20.000Z","msg":"何必呢, 買個二手harddisk都唔是太貴啫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a4f4279d92eec0e7fc2c658f97b29edf80c0ae","tid":481808,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何必呢, 買個二手harddisk都唔是太貴啫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正如有人有Mac 唔用要MacBook  裝Linux<br />\n你環得人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申用緊 iMac 行Linux"},{"pid":"8f9d4d09606d29c1b5e886e011cd5a4c30342ed4","tid":481808,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"順便問 依家啲機既bios 有個係用LAN boot既選項 其實點樣用"},{"pid":"7b424c75aed45670d68278ebcedf6ad5f906b0ef","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便問 依家啲機既bios 有個係用LAN boot既選項 其實點樣用</blockquote><br />\nPXE Server boot機，可以<br />\n<br />\na) 用嚟慳返入碟裝os嘅時間，自己連個server然後自動裝<br />\n<br />\nb) 用嚟做集中管理，有咩更新server搞就得唔駛逐部搞<br />\n<br />\nc) 去盡啲，索性diskless workstation，直頭啲電腦連硬碟都唔駛裝，所有野network做晒，然後熄機就乜都冇晒，適合學校、網吧、公眾場所或者公司共用電腦用<br />\n<br />\n一般都係網絡環境入面有好多部腦要管理先會set嘅"},{"pid":"6690e8305eb6711e0985b86e4e1948e8f546dfa0","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用usb手指啦</blockquote><br />\n唔想無限抽插"},{"pid":"9a2bd93af9626f682b747887a009dab2e569788e","tid":481808,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 不過budget有限打算唔買harddisk亦唔諗住買Windows</blockquote><br />\n冇錢搞咁撚多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bac798d94fe2a806476b349db6bb765c0a84db","tid":481808,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote> 不過budget有限打算唔買harddisk亦唔諗住買Windows</blockquote><br />\n冇錢搞咁撚多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>喺電腦效能同埋買硬碟之間取捨啫"}]}